Package: dailymet
Type: Package
Title: Utility Functions to Model Daily Meteorological Variables
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Yves Deville  
Maintainer: Yves Deville <deville.yves@alpestat.com>
Description: Provide utility functions to model meteorological variables
